It does not plead to paragraph 1 thereof because: 




 1.1 under s 14ZZO of the Taxation Administration Act 1953 the Applicant has the burden of proving that the assessment for the year ended 30 June 1998 is excessive; 
 1.2 the matters referred to in paragraphs 4 --- 15 and 18 --- 29 of the Respondent's Statement of Facts Issues and Contentions dated 25 May 2005 are matters in respect of which the Applicant bears the burden of proof.
